             were indicted for <rs id="t17880227-4-off14" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17880227-4-off14" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17880227-4-off14" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17880227-4-victim71" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Smith
                        <interp inst="t17880227-4-victim71" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
